snippet.title: Impeached - Trailer
snippet.description:
Become the President. Sign executive orders. Bull S#@t your way through press meetings. Getting Impeached has never been so much fun!

PLAY HERE: goo.gl/Y5cVu8

Impeached is a fun little game made by OddBird Studio during a local game jam. We wanted to experiment with a fun idea and the theme was Fake News. 

If you liked this game be sure to check out the game we are currently working on called Arrow Heads! Links down below. =)

Website: http://oddbirdstudio.ca/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/oddbirdstudio

Enjoy!
